actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on yellow 577 stage, 5-{4-[4-[4-(4,8-disulfonaphthalen-2-ylazo)-phenylamino]-6-(2-sulfoethylamino)-[1,3,5]triazin-2-ylamino]phenylazo}isophthalic acid/sodium salt.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 2007, the duty on a certain chemical.

titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on yellow 577 stage, 5-{4-[4-[4-(4,8-disulfonaphthalen-2-ylazo)-phenylamino]-6-(2-sulfoethylamino)-[1,3,5]triazin-2-ylamino]phenylazo}isophthalic acid/sodium salt.
